procstep.procdesc:
This data layer was downloaded from Thinkburst Media, Inc at http://data.geocomm.com/catalog/US/61093/group111.htm. When downloaded, the layer was an E00 interchange file, and GeoPlan converted it to an ArcInfo coverage. The data layer was then converted into a shapefile and projected from North American Datum 1983 to FGDL HPGN and overlaid on a 1999 doqq file for the State of Florida. Discrepancies between the placement of power transmission lines in the shapefile and the location of power transmission lines on the 1999 doqq file were remedied by aligning the features in the shapefile with the power transmission lines on the 1999 doqq file at a scale of 1:24,000. Process Date: 20051200
GeoPlan, during the QA/QC process included the following aspects:
-added [EDIT_TYPE] field based on whether the line was "moved" or "created," or whether the location of the line on the doqq was undetectable, or "N/A."
-added [DESCRIPT] field based on [UTLNTYPE] and information provided by source.
-added [FGDLAQDATE] field based on the date FGDL acquired the data from the source.
